   *Mental Health Innovation*: This kind of brain-behavior mapping could
   one day complement (not replace) traditional mental health assessments,
   offering a more objective and science-based tool for intervention.

* Big Picture Impact*

This study supports the idea that there=E2=80=99s a deep link between how o=
